<header>
  <h1>Medirectory</h1>
  <p>Find a healthcare provider.</p>
  <div class="search-bar">
    {{#if basicSearch}}
      {{#basic-search submit='submit' placeholder='Try "camille houston" or "williams portland"'}}
      <button {{action 'advanced'}}> Advanced Search </button>
      {{/basic-search}}
    {{else}}
      {{#advanced-search submit='submit' name=name location=location taxonomy=taxonomy npi=npi organization=organization}}
        <button {{action 'basic'}}> Basic Search </button>
      {{/advanced-search}}
    {{/if}}
  </div>
</header>

<div class="about">
  <h2>What is Medirectory?</h2>
  <p>Medirectory is a pilot project by The MITRE Corporation. The project is open source and its code can be accessed at <a href="https://github.com/Medirectory" alt="Source code for Medirectory">https://github.com/Medirectory</a>.</p>
</div>

